Text::Convert::PETSCII Version 0.03
===================================

Text::Convert::PETSCII provides basic methods for converting text format between
ASCII and PETSCII character sets.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

